  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1415553">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1415553/" class="title-link">既然没有调查就没有发言权--那就调查啊！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1415553"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jeffwang1840/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2525848-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jeffwang1840/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Jeff@W</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-21"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-21 03:38:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1415553_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  对毛泽东的评价似乎这些年在网上越来越激烈了，但你不得不承认，在那些反对毛泽东的人当中没有几个人真正读过他的著作，更鲜有人去读马克思的著作了。 不是说要实事求是吗？你连人家的文章都没看上几篇，却靠着一些道听途说来批评，不得不让人产生这些观点的可信程度。 无论是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1415553/#comments">(13回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">21有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1415553_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1415553_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



